Generate Allure reports for BDD Test results

Step 1:
pip install allure-behave

Step 2:

$ behave -f allure_behave.formatter:AllureFormatter -o %allure_result_folder%

Step 3:
Download Allure Command Line Server

Step 4 :
allure serve %allure_result_folder%

behave
behave Features/Github.feature --no-capture -f allure_behave.formatter:AllureFormatter -o AllureReports
behave Features/BookAPI.feature --no-capture
behave Features/BookAPI.feature --no-capture --tags=smoke

open allure json report